ATMA SUDDHI - Yoga School Management System
Copyright (C) 2025 Javier Ballesteros

This program is a comprehensive management system for yoga schools,
developed specifically for Atma Suddhi - Espacio de Yoga.

Features include:
- Student management
- Class scheduling and attendance
- Individual yoga therapy sessions (Yogaterapia)
- Payment tracking
- Calendar management
- Accounting module
- File management for therapy sessions
- User management and roles

For more information about this software, please contact:
Javier Ballesteros
Email: javierb507@gmail.com
Project: https://github.com/javierb507/yoga-school-management